<div class="hgroup"><h1 class="title"><span class="title">通用辅助功能</span></h1></div>
<div class="region">
<div class="contents"><p class="p">Unity 桌面包含帮助有不同障碍或特殊需求用户的辅助技术，能够与常用的辅助设备进行交互，多数功能可以在<span class="gui">系统设置</span>的<span class="gui">辅助功能</span>中找到。</p></div>
<div id="vision" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">视觉障碍</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">失明</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-braille.html" title="使用盲文阅读屏幕">使用盲文阅读屏幕</a><span class="desc"> — 使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 屏幕阅读器在盲文显示机上显示。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-screen-reader.html" title="朗读屏幕">朗读屏幕</a><span class="desc"> — 使用 <span class="app">Orca</span> 屏幕阅读器朗读用户界面。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">弱视</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-font-size.html" title="更改屏幕上的文字大小">更改屏幕上的文字大小</a><span class="desc"> — 使用较大字体使文本更易于阅读。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-cursor-blink.html" title="让键盘光标闪烁">让键盘光标闪烁</a><span class="desc"> — 让插入点闪烁并控制其闪烁速度。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-contrast.html" title="调整对比度">调整对比度</a><span class="desc"> — 让屏幕上的窗口和按钮层次分明，以便更好地区分它们。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="sound" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">听觉障碍</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents"><div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner"><div class="region"><ul><li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-visualalert.html" title="警告声响起时屏幕闪烁">警告声响起时屏幕闪烁</a><span class="desc"> — 播放警告声时，启用视觉警告：屏幕或窗口闪烁。</span>
</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div>
</div></div>
<div id="mobility" class="sect"><div class="inner">
<div class="hgroup"><h2 class="title"><span class="title">运动障碍</span></h2></div>
<div class="region"><div class="contents">
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">鼠标移动</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-mousekeys.html" title="使用小键盘点击和移动鼠标指针。">使用小键盘点击和移动鼠标指针。</a><span class="desc"> — 启用鼠标键，通过小键盘控制鼠标。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-sensitivity.html" title="调整鼠标和触摸板速度">调整鼠标和触摸板速度</a><span class="desc"> — 使用鼠标或触摸板时更改指针移动速度。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">点击和拖动</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-right-click.html" title="模拟右键点击">模拟右键点击</a><span class="desc"> — 按住鼠标左键完成右击。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="mouse-doubleclick.html" title="调整双击速度">调整双击速度</a><span class="desc"> — 控制两次按下鼠标键的行为被识别为双击操作的速度。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-dwellclick.html" title="通过悬停模拟点击">通过悬停模拟点击</a><span class="desc"> — “悬停点击”功能使您能够通过保持鼠标不动完成点击。</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
</div></div>
<div class="links topiclinks"><div class="inner">
<div class="title title-links"><h3><span class="title">键盘使用</span></h3></div>
<div class="region"><ul>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-osk.html" title="使用屏幕键盘">使用屏幕键盘</a><span class="desc"> — 通过使用鼠标点击屏幕键盘来输入文字。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-bouncekeys.html" title="开启回弹键">开启回弹键</a><span class="desc"> — 忽略对同一个键的快速重复按键动作。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-slowkeys.html" title="开启慢速键">开启慢速键</a><span class="desc"> — 按键之后，屏幕显示对应字母之前，有一些延迟。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="a11y-stickykeys.html" title="开启粘滞键">开启粘滞键</a><span class="desc"> — 按键盘快捷键时一次按一个键，而无需一次按住所有键。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-repeat-keys.html" title="禁用重复键">禁用重复键</a><span class="desc"> — 让键盘在按住键时不重复字母，或更改每个键的延迟和重复速度。</span>
</li>
<li class="links ">
<a href="keyboard-nav.html" title="键盘导航">键盘导航</a><span class="desc"> — 在没有鼠标的情况下单击和移动鼠标指针</span>
</li>
</ul></div>
